claim.claim-text:
12. A system for generating automobile insurance certificates from a remote computer terminal connected by a computer network to a central computer, comprising: 
a remote computer terminal; 
a central computer; 
a database stored on said central computer in which data relating to automobile insurance policies are stored; 
a software interface for viewing data stored in said database from said remote computer terminal; and 
a computer network connecting said remote computer terminal with said central computer; 
wherein said software interface allows a user of said remote computer terminal to identify an expiring automobile insurance policy by viewing on said remote computer terminal data, stored on said central computer, relating to expiring policies; and 
wherein, said software interface allows the user of said remote computer terminal to order electronically, in response to the identification of the expiring policy, an automobile insurance certificate from said remote computer terminal relating to the expiring policy.
